Billie Jean - Stalk the Stalker (Quickie)

Materials
Copper Tape
Pencil
Circuit Stickers LEDs
A4 sheets
Coin cell
Sound Sensor Effect sticker
Self Adhesive two way acrylic mirror



Tools:
Eraser
Sharpener

#1 - Draw shape for sound sensor 
#2 - Get another A4 sheet and apply the copper tape
#3 - Apply the LEDs on the copper tape
#4 - Apply sound sensor 
#5 - Put coin cell to the copper tape
#6 - Apply mirror over steps 2 to 5 and apply to the ceiling
